{"tid":455249,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"FG 第一份工唔夠3個月 寫唔寫落CV?","createTime":"2017-11-02T02:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T07:28:32.000Z","uid":55008,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa95781d89fcf3c49859edbc43bc82ef208911b","tid":455249,"uid":55008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:15:27.000Z","msg":"fg 8月搵到第一份工<br />\n因為同老闆又唔夾 關係好差 <br />\n最終佢唔比我過試用 要自願resign左<br />\n<br />\n唯一一樣好擔心 唔知下一步應該點做?<br />\n答做左半年pt又唔係<br />\n話放左半年假又唔係<br />\n答左做2.5個月ft又死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好擔心<br />\n求指教"},{"pid":"5b00d04a401de4e8457944702cdbf2885a7106f9","tid":455249,"uid":89955,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"唔寫 interview講最近先搵工"},{"pid":"2cf7cf6ccf495f5cdf98b46c02c2b6747b7579a0","tid":455249,"uid":8014,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"話去左daddy 公司美國總部學野<br />\n<br />\n今次回流係daddy 叫我番香港去uncle 公司幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3469769e9bad658351e7b229f8486e44937121","tid":455249,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗寫"},{"pid":"0d76eb9024657cf8ffe512d1b51f6ad7d1c9bc82","tid":455249,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:01:33.000Z","msg":"grad trip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a753869c4f0fd3435b2f78bc001467efda019451","tid":455249,"uid":37474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fg 8月搵到第一份工<br />\n因為同老闆又唔夾 關係好差 <br />\n最終佢唔比我過試用 要自願resign左<br />\n<br />\n唯一一樣好擔心 唔知下一步應該點做?<br />\n答做左半年pt又唔係<br />\n話放左半年假又唔係<b