ockquote><br />\n咁好既 佢幫你寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司講明 做多過半年先有"},{"pid":"97a29527de1d89aecaa573dcc3a6718ab2ca149e","tid":455249,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都做左2.5月，不過係自己resign，公司連水都慳，要我地自己煲水。<br />\n<br />\n我有吖head幫我寫reference letter 我先寫落CV</blockquote><br />\n咁好既 佢幫你寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司講明 做多過半年先有</blockquote><br />\n其實無乜意思, 咁短可以寫乜, 唔通話公司無錢請人咩"},{"pid":"0d1f99baa2593f71d00b928fa3baf2ef1af6487f","tid":455249,"uid":68728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫，好過白紙小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過唔到試用期仲衰過冇經驗啦"},{"pid":"78d28c4af5320b135ea9526422c8aa81a72fe9b6","tid":455249,"uid":139422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都做左2.5月，不過係自己resign，公司連水都慳，要我地自己煲水。<br />\n<br />\n我有吖head幫我寫reference letter 我先寫落CV</blockquote><br />\n咁好既 佢幫你寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司講明 做多過半年先有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直屬上司好人，腦細仆街。"},{"pid":"acb1f7bfd1a1a03f2e1222a61083b3ef7bd3c17b","tid":455249,"uid":139422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都做左2.5月，不過係自己resign，公司連水都慳，要我地自己煲水。<br />\n<br />\n我有吖head幫我寫reference letter 我先寫落CV</blockquote><br />\n咁好既 佢幫你寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司講明 做多過半年先有</blockquote><br />\n其實無乜意思, 咁短可以寫乜, 唔通話公司無錢請人咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比人炒係寫都無謂，但如果係自己走，都可以既。"},{"pid":"95342e75f6f9228e0207347cd75b4d4b9188d556","tid":455249,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:58:40.000Z","msg":"咪寫，整花張cv<br />\n利申：fg 第一份做咗一個月自願離職，之後一直當冇做過冇落cv"},{"pid":"2c